        Discover fresh-cut flowers, heirloom plants, and the joy of bringing nature home.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="/products" class="btn btn-primary">Shop Our Blooms</a>
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn-secondary">Our Story</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gallery Preview -->
  <section class="gallery-preview">
    <div class="gallery-grid">
      <img src="/Images/colorful-mixed-bouquet-vase.jpeg" alt="Colorful mixed flower bouquet" />
      <img src="/Images/pink-zinnias-bouquet-field.jpeg" alt="Pink zinnias in the field" />
      <img src="/Images/butterfly.jpeg" alt="Butterfly on zinnias" />
      <img src="/Images/spring-bouquet-snapdragons-larkspur.jpeg" alt="Spring bouquet with snapdragons" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section class="features">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Why Choose Us</h2>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">ðŸŒ±</div>
          <h3>Locally Grown</h3>
          <p>All our flowers and plants are grown right here on our farm, ensuring the freshest blooms for your home.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">ðŸŒ¿</div>
          <h3>Sustainable Practices</h3>
          <p>We use organic methods and sustainable farming practices to nurture our plants and protect the earth.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">ðŸ’š</div>
          <h3>Grown with Love</h3>
          <p>Each plant receives individual care and attention, from seed to bloom, ensuring exceptional quality.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Seasonal Highlights -->
  <section class="seasonal">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Seasonal Favorites</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Discover what's blooming in our gardens right now</p>
      <div class="product-grid">
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="product-image">
            <img src="/Images/zinnia-arrangement-ceramic-vase.jpeg" alt="Zinnia arrangement" />
          </div>
          <h3>Mixed Zinnias</h3>
          <p>Vibrant, colorful zinnias perfect for any occasion</p>
          <span class="price">$24.99 / bunch</span>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="product-image">
            <img src="/Images/snapdragons-garden-rows.jpeg" alt="Snapdragons" />
          </div>
          <h3>Snapdragons</h3>
          <p>Tall, elegant blooms in sunset colors</p>
          <span class="price">$18.99 / bunch</span>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="product-image">
            <img src="/Images/pink-clematis-vine-blooms.jpeg" alt="Clematis" />
          </div>
          <h3>Clematis</h3>
          <p>Stunning pink vine flowers for elegant arrangements</p>
          <span class="price">$32.99 / dozen</span>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="product-image">
            <img src="/Images/white-dahlia-arrangement-mason-jar.jpeg" alt="White dahlias" />
          </div>
          <h3>White Dahlias</h3>
          <p>Classic white blooms with delicate greenery</p>
          <span class="price">$28.99 / bunch</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="section-cta">
        <a href="/products" class="btn btn-primary">View All Products</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonial Section -->
  <section class="testimonial">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="testimonial-content">
        <blockquote>
          "Barefoot Flower Farms has transformed my home with their stunning arrangements.
          The quality and freshness of their flowers is unmatched. I'm a customer for life!"
        </blockquote>
